query:
SET @sac_id = (SELECT id FROM counties WHERE name LIKE '%Sacramento County%' AND state = 'California' LIMIT 1);

-- More Sacramento County EMS Adult Treatment Policies
INSERT INTO protocolChunks (countyId, protocolNumber, protocolTitle, section, content, sourcePdfUrl, protocolEffectiveDate, protocolYear, createdAt)
VALUES 
(@sac_id, '8060', 'Stroke', 'Medical', 'Sacramento County EMS Treatment Policy for Stroke. Stroke screening, last known well time documentation, and stroke center transport.', 'https://dhs.saccounty.gov/PUB/EMS/Documents/PoliciesProceduresProtocols/8000/PP-8060.pdf', '2025-06-01', 2025, NOW()),
(@sac_id, '8062', 'Behavioral Crisis/Restraint', 'Medical', 'Sacramento County EMS Treatment Policy for Behavioral Crisis and Restraint. De-escalation and chemical restraint.', 'https://dhs.saccounty.gov/PUB/EMS/Documents/PoliciesProceduresProtocols/8000/PP-8062.pdf', '2025-06-01', 2025, NOW()),
(@sac_id, '8063', 'Nausea and Vomiting', 'Medical', 'Sacramento County EMS Treatment Policy for Nausea and Vomiting. Ondansetron administration.', 'https://dhs.saccounty.gov/PUB/EMS/Documents/PoliciesProceduresProtocols/8000/PP-8063.pdf', '2025-06-01', 2025, NOW()),
(@sac_id, '8065', 'Hemorrhage', 'Trauma', 'Sacramento County EMS Treatment Policy for Hemorrhage. Hemorrhage control techniques and TXA.', 'https://dhs.saccounty.gov/PUB/EMS/Documents/PoliciesProceduresProtocols/8000/PP-8065.pdf', '2025-06-01', 2025, NOW()),
(@sac_id, '8066', 'Pain Management', 'Medical', 'Sacramento County EMS Treatment Policy for Pain Management. Fentanyl and morphine administration guidelines.', 'https://dhs.saccounty.gov/PUB/EMS/Documents/PoliciesProceduresProtocols/8000/PP-8066.pdf', '2025-12-01', 2025, NOW()),
(@sac_id, '8067', 'Sepsis/Septic Shock', 'Medical', 'Sacramento County EMS Treatment Policy for Sepsis and Septic Shock. Early recognition and fluid resuscitation.', 'https://dhs.saccounty.gov/PUB/EMS/Documents/PoliciesProceduresProtocols/8000/PP-8067.pdf', '2025-06-01', 2025, NOW()),
(@sac_id, '8068', 'General Medical Complaint', 'Medical', 'Sacramento County EMS Treatment Policy for General Medical Complaint. Assessment and supportive care.', 'https://dhs.saccounty.gov/PUB/EMS/Documents/PoliciesProceduresProtocols/8000/PP-8068.pdf', '2025-06-01', 2025, NOW()),
(@sac_id, '8069', 'Buprenorphine', 'Medical', 'Sacramento County EMS Treatment Policy for Buprenorphine. Considerations for patients on MAT.', 'https://dhs.saccounty.gov/PUB/EMS/Documents/PoliciesProceduresProtocols/8000/PP-8069.pdf', '2025-06-01', 2025, NOW()),
